name: You Are Better
description: Released 10/19/04 You Are Better, the sophomore album from Jacob's Well featuring 13 original songs Produced by Rob Loomis & Jacob's Well. The album was recorded at Trillium Lane Studios in Seattle WA, and mixed/mastered by Masaki Liu (Five Minute Walk Records, Justin McRoberts) at One Way Studio in Benicia CA. Track Listing 1. Taste & See 2. Lamedh 3. Psalm 3 4. Not Ashamed 5. Abide 6. Sands 7. I Will Praise You 8. All In All 9. Song Of Repentance 10. We Worship You 11. We Come 12. Psalm 61 13. You Are Better

name: Be Still
description: Released 03/15/02 Jacob's Well's original debut release. Recorded in October of 2001 over a period of 4 days at Sound Town Digital in Dallas, TX. Produced by Shane Everett and Shane Barnard. Track Listing 1. Prelude 2. We Worship You 3. Humbled 4. Search Me O God 5. I Have Come 6. I Shall Not Be Moved 7. Be Still 8. Precious Blood 9. Maranatha 10. As I Bow * This album is available on iTunes, Zune and Amazon.com

name: Moments
description: Released 12/15/03 Moments is a collection of original songs composed and recorded by Rob Loomis at home. What makes this album rare is that with the exception of 3 songs, no song had been previously written prior to the recording. What you hear are the unrehearsed moments of music played one night in August 2003. A must have for fans of Jim Brickman and George Winston. Track Listing 1. Fall Wind 2. Dreams 3. Sunrise 4. Conversations 5. A Child's Day 6. Elise 7. Song Of Repentance 8. Surrender 9. Goodbyes
